method CREATE_XL_RELATIONSHIPS.


** Constant node name
  DATA: lc_xml_node_relationships TYPE string VALUE 'Relationships',
        lc_xml_node_relationship  TYPE string VALUE 'Relationship',
        " Node attributes
        lc_xml_attr_id            TYPE string VALUE 'Id',
